<p><div class="description">Description</div>The DC16 Web badge is network solution. The DC16 doesn't have any means to talk directly over IP, nor could it affectively run an IP stack (given the coders motivation to write one). Below is a network diagram and explanation of each piece required to make the DC16 Web-badge a reality.</p>

