<p><div class="description">DC16 Serial Interface</div>HTTP/1.1 is a very simple interface. The DC16 provides the bare minimum that still allows a standard web browser to talk. When a client sends a requests, the GET line is the only one that is read. From this line the DC16 attempts to find the requested file on the SD memory card. A basic response is crafted and sent back to the user.</p>

